cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.Medical Imaging, cs.NE 

The paper discusses the use of deep learning algorithms for image recognition in the field of automated carcinoma detection in confocal laser endomicroscopy (CLE) images. This falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with medical imaging (cs.Medical Imaging) and neural networks (cs.NE).
